{
  "stem": "1062.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I said, we were marched out to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Marched out from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as we were going, you know, the snow piled up because I had wooden-- leather shoes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when the-- when you have a lump on your foot, and it's wood, so you start going like a duck.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You could clean it up sometimes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But what happened, people didn't have enough strength.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after a while, they would just sit down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Once you sat down in the-- everybody passed through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the-- from behind, there was a-- there was German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They would shoot you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Once you stayed behind, they kill you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, in my transport, I personally didn't see it, but somebody told me and I remember this, that one German sat down, a German soldier, took his rifle, put it in his mouth and pulled the trigger.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He killed himself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Yeah, he killed himself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Apparently he was a good Nazi.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I want you to know what happened to me up to this point, and I'm talking 1945, is nothing compared to what's going to happen now.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That night-- the following day-- we marched all night, all night, all night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The following day we marched and one night we came to a place called Nikolaev.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was a big, big farm over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was one, one, one house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "One building, like a barn or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I went into the barn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And everybody tried to get into that barn, but there was no room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the barn, they had some beams across.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I climbed up and I sat on the beam.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE], whoever wanted to go on the beam, sat on the beam.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was like a beam across.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "An SS officer walks in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had a sub machine gun, shoots down everybody from the beam, just like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I saw him-- he started on this end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I, I, I jumped off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I fell down on the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the morning, I got up and I knew people that were in main camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I saw people standing outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember man with stubbles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The stubbles were white, like frozen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the men was staying there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They looked like alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was one guy, his name was Pincus.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I walked over to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said, Pincus, I said to him, and I just gave him a little push and he turned over.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They froze to death standing up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were-- they looked, they looked alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Well, we stayed there over, over that night, and then they start pushing us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we went to a place called Gleiwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Gleiwitz was the first German town, which was on the Polish-German border.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We went through a town called Katowice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "From Nikolaev, we went to a town called Kattowitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Today, it's called Katowice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Katowice today is the capital of Silesia, of lower Silesia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It's a big city today.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There the coal mines are, the coal, the coal area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Very rich in minerals.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I went-- when I went through it, it was a small, a small little town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I-- when I went through Katowice, we went through the, the center of town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I see children and civilians inside the building, because nobody was on the streets, because when Jews-- when we arrived to a station, they would make an announcement.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[GERMAN] You know, a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So everybody ran away, because the Jews were like, you know, like, like, a [NON-ENGLISH], like, like, like, like a plague was coming.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So everybody-- you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They were all inside the-- inside the houses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I saw children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I saw civilians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So it brought me back a little memories, you know, from, from, from civilian life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We went to Katowice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then we came into a town called Gleiwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Gleiwitz was already in the-- see, Kattowitz was on the Polish side-- at one time, not today.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Before the War, Kattowitz was on the Polish side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Gleiwitz was on the German side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we were in Gleiwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then they brought in trains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "No, they took us out to the rail station there, to a railroad station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And there were trains.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But the trains, they were not enclosed trains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They were open.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They were open trains.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They were not cattle cars, they were like freight cars, open, halfway open.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And they put us-- they pushed the thing into those cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And the trains started to move.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And the train moved to Prague.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I remember we passed through Prague towards Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "But we didn't eat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "We didn't have no food.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
